org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.ietf.params.xml.ns.yang.ietf.netconf.monitoring.rev101004.netconf.state.datastores.datastore.locks.lock.type.partial.lock

Interface PartialLock

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<PartialLock>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Locks>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<PartialLockKey>, LockInfo

    public interface PartialLock
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Locks>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<PartialLock>, LockInfo, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<PartialLockKey>
    List of partial locks.

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module ietf-netconf-monitoring
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/ietf-netconf-monitoring.yang): 

     list partial-lock {
     key "lock-id"
     leaf lock-id {
         type uint32;
     }
     leaf locked-by-session {
         type uint32;
     }
     leaf locked-time {
         type date-and-time;
     }
     leaf-list select {
         type xpath1.0;
     }
     leaf-list locked-node {
         type instance-identifier;
     }
     uses netconf-state;
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is ietf-netconf-monitoring/netconf-state/datastores/datastore/locks/lock-type/partial-lock/partial-lock

    To create instances of this class use PartialLockBuilder.
